#

Lobster Thermidor with Truffle Risotto

50 min
$50
800 kcal
Difficulty: 60%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeSeafoodHigh Protein

Cuisine:

FrenchItalian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

ElegantSpecial OccasionComfort Food

Description

A luxurious dish featuring succulent lobster in a creamy, cheesy sauce with a hint of truffle in the risotto, perfect for a special occasion!

Ingredients

  • lobster tails: 2
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • shallots: 1, minced
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • dijon mustard: 1 tablespoon
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • truffle oil: 1 tablespoon
  • arborio rice: 1 cup
  • chicken broth: 4 cups
  • fresh parsley: for garnish
